ormal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n亂晒章<br />\n<br />\n如果真心想回購 駛乜停牌<br />\n<br />\n愈跌愈買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822bdbfdf53ea217e9afb786a923eb8645ae0575","tid":253202,"uid":54993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:55:49.000Z","msg":"條友係電話會議咁樣覆法, 造假既機會都幾大<br />\n轉移視線, 陰謀論, 反向批評番沽空機構數據來源(其實工商檔案幾百蚊就拎到, 有咩來源可以懷疑), 答唔到就賴其他野<br />\n<br />\n睇怕危危地"},{"pid":"3c83aa4ab106e5b15e61905f5817a91687db6f3c","tid":253202,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友係電話會議咁樣覆法, 造假既機會都幾大<br />\n轉移視線, 陰謀論, 反向批評番沽空機構數據來源(其實工商檔案幾百蚊就拎到, 有咩來源可以懷疑), 答唔到就賴其他野<br />\n<br />\n睇怕危危地</blockquote><br />\n淘X都有得買成交量啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4941a9651455b161337c29500982a1f47415a7cf","tid":253202,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"對沽空報告有心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1676888968f2a46f47bc221ee0d811805780f5","tid":253202,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:28:22.000Z","msg":"【股價跟跌】慧聰網澄清 已高價沽售大部分科通芯城持股<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170522/large/1495459387_651d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170522%2Flarge%2F1495459387_651d.jpg&h=948e02c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受科通芯城被沽空機構狙擊拖累，慧聰網（2280）今股價跌8%，收報6.16元。<br />\n<br />\n公司發公告指，收到多名股東、投資者查詢公司於科通芯城（400）的持股情況。慧聰網指，科通芯城上市時，作為基礎投資者認購其股份，以總代價1.55億元獲發3875萬股（佔當時已發行股本2.82%），每股作價4元。截至今日，公司已出售大部分持股，平均出售價格11.9元，遠高於認購價。以此推算，料公司帳面賺約2億元。目前尚餘1300萬股持股。<br />\n<br />\n慧聰網行政總裁兼執行董事郭江又於日內增持公司股份，從公開市場買入20萬股，代價131萬元。完成後，郭 江及配偶持股增至1.26億股，即佔12.63%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56728645&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56728645%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170522&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7B0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=baf4396d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56728645%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170522&h=5209483f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56728645&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170522</a>"}]}